item.title: The Beginning
item.description: This world is made. It begins, the realm is set in Calumnia. The points converge.

item.title: Photon Blaster
item.description: “Pew Pew!” - Photon Blaster The photon blaster is a rare, futuristic weapon which consumes Battery Packs to shoot photon blasts.

item.title: Calumnia
item.description: The medieval fantasy world in which the players begin. This place is full of Dragons, magic, kings, queens, and other fantastic things.

item.title: Sierra
item.description: Sierra plays a halfling rogue, named Maerix Armnik. Maerix is chaotic evil, and is the Yang to Bella’s Yin.

item.title: Bella
item.description: Bella plays a Goliath named Ashy’l Maabu, a Goliath Rogue who stole a working time machine, which sent her into the past. She wields a Photon Blaster.

item.title: Battery Packs
item.description: Battery Packs are a rare item used to charge the Photon Blaster. They contain 100% battery power.

item.title: Elise
item.description: Elise plays a Human. She is a Warlock that serves an Archfey.
